---- NEWK
Shift-Alt-P     (Show IDE)
Shift-Alt-Q     (Exit IDE)

Shift-Alt-1     (Show window 1: REPL)
Shift-Alt-2     (Show window 2: git diff)
Shift-Alt-3     (Show window 3: stack build) Compiler
Shift-Alt-4     (Show window 4: Command - git) To give orders
Shift-Alt-5     (Show window 5: KATA editor) Emacs
Shift-Alt-7     (Show window 7: Navegator) Abrowser

Shift-Alt-+     (xterm: Zoom in)

newk -s         (Show all kataficated solutions)

--- EMACS
M-X column-number-mode
C-X C-+    (Zoom in)
M-P        (Save all)
---- Emacs Dante (Haskell)
M-X dante-restart
C-C .      (type of selection)
C-U C-C .  (insert types)

